article.description: — Laurynas Vaistaras had 13 points in Campbell's 65-58 victory against The Citadel on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Vaistaras' 13 help Campbell knock off The Citadel 65-58
article.linkText: Vaistaras' 13 help Campbell knock off The Citadel 65-58
article.story: BUIES CREEK, N.C. -- — Laurynas Vaistaras had 13 points in Campbell's 65-58 victory against The Citadel on Wednesday night. Vaistaras shot 4 for 8 (2 for 3 from 3-point range) and 3 of 4 from the free throw line for the Fighting Camels (2-4). Anthony Dell'Orso added 10 points while shooting 3 for 8, including 2 for 3 from beyond the arc, and he also had 10 rebounds. Jasin Sinani had nine points and finished 3 of 5 from 3-point range. Elijah Morgan finished with 16 points and seven rebounds for the Bulldogs (3-4). Winston Hill added 13 points and eight rebounds for The Citadel. In addition, AJ Smith finished with 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
